Star-shaped, heart-shaped pimple patches do look cute — but are they really doing the job? That’s the question we kept coming back to while working on Touch Me Not 😌

We discovered that hydrocolloid works BEST in its purest form, so we skipped the cute and went for pimple patches that are invisibly thin, matte, and have ingredients that actually work while you sleep 💤 

So no, our patches may not win design awards.
But they will win against breakouts. And honestly, that’s the only win that matters 💖

Ever wondered what your skincare ingredients actually do once they hit your skin?👀
We broke it down — no jargon, no over-complication.

✨ Hyaluronic Acid → Pulls in hydration, gives you that soft, bouncy feel
🧘‍♀️ Niacinamide → Calms redness, evens out skin, keeps oil in check
🧼 Salicylic Acid → Clears out pores and keeps breakouts from crashing your plans
☀️ Vitamin C → Brightens skin and helps fade dark spots over time

They may be small on your shelf, but these ingredients do the heavy lifting for your skin🏋🏻
